data.title: Justin Moore, 9/13
data.text:
Justin Moore With Special Guest Tenille Arts

Get tickets here: Justin Moore Live in Concert | State Farm Center

Multi-PLATINUM hitmaker Justin Moore has built a loyal following over the past decade with his traditional country sound and captivating live shows. The Arkansas native just notched his twelfth No. 1 with “You, Me, and Whiskey,” a smoldering duet with Priscilla Block. Over his decade-plus year career, Moore’s No. 1 hits have included “Point at You,” “Lettin’ The Night Roll,” “If Heaven Wasn’t So Far Away,” “Small Town USA,” and “Till My Last Day,” as well as various PLATINUM-certified albums and singles. The Valory Music Co. recording artist has earned multiple ACM, ACA, People’s Choice, and ACC Awards nominations, as well as an ACM Award win.
